opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 17th day of July, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Mandamus Relief and or Extraordinary Relief and Petition to Amend Petition for Writ of Mandamus are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
